query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('amazon-cognito',
'andengine',
'fancybox-2',
'ioexception',
'kerberos',
'kinect',
'line-breaks',
'monogame',
'oracle-adf',
'plsqldeveloper',
'python-multithreading',
'restlet',
'smack',
'timepicker');
